        "duration": 1.374
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm imagining like,\npicking up a piece of dust",
        "start": 626.26,
        "duration": 2.37
    },
    {
        "text": "with the tweezers off of\nyour desk and being like, OK.",
        "start": 628.63,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "I'm going to learn all\nabout the outer layer of it",
