        "duration": 0.499
    },
    {
        "text": "That's exactly it, though.",
        "start": 638.71,
        "duration": 0.73
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah.",
        "start": 639.44,
        "duration": 0.62
    },
    {
        "text": "It's really cool.",
        "start": 640.06,
        "duration": 1.186
    },
    {
        "text": "It's amazing we can say\nall this stuff, yeah.",
